{"tid":842304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美內政部:必要時進行海上封鎖以阻礙俄羅斯出口能源","createTime":"2018-09-30T07:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T00:10:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"013f35674281b49da826c9059c71947d529a0c4e","tid":842304,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"美內政部:必要時進行海上封鎖以阻礙俄羅斯出口能源<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180930/0/2/2/%e7%be%8e%e5%85%a7%e6%94%bf%e9%83%a8-%e5%bf%85%e8%a6%81%e6%99%82%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c%e6%b5%b7%e4%b8%8a%e5%b0%81%e9%8e%96%e4%bb%a5%e9%98%bb%e7%a4%99%e4%bf%84%e7%be%85%e6%96%af%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90-9283880.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F0%2F2%2F2%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%2585%25a7%25e6%2594%25bf%25e9%2583%25a8-%25e5%25bf%2585%25e8%25a6%2581%25e6%2599%2582%25e9%2580%25b2%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%25b0%2581%25e9%258e%2596%25e4%25bb%25a5%25e9%2598%25bb%25e7%25a4%2599%25e4%25bf%2584%25e7%25be%2585%25e6%2596%25af%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%258f%25a3%25e8%2583%25bd%25e6%25ba%2590-9283880.html&d=Wm750lrdtaPfKF5rJEqd0l0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=2ae05c44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20180930/0/2/2/%e7%be%8e%e5%85%a7%e6%94%bf%e9%83%a8-%e5%bf%85%e8%a6%81%e6%99%82%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c%e6%b5%b7%e4%b8%8a%e5%b0%81%e9%8e%96%e4%bb%a5%e9%98%bb%e7%a4%99%e4%bf%84%e7%be%85%e6%96%af%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90-9283880.html</a><br />\n<br />\n　　【環球網綜合報導】據俄新社9月30日援引美國《華盛頓觀察家報》消息，美國內政部長津克28日稱，如有必要，美國可對俄羅斯進行海上封鎖，以阻止其向市場供應能源。<br />\n<br />\n　　津克當天在參加美國匹茲堡的一次工業活動時說：&ldquo;美國海軍有能力保障海路通航，必要時也可以進行封鎖，阻止（俄羅斯的）能源進入市場。&rdquo;他認為，俄羅斯的經濟狀況取決於其能源出口。俄羅斯在中東實行積極的政策，目的是向中東地區出口自己的石油和天然氣，就像其在歐洲的能源出口一樣。<br />\n<br />\n　　津克稱，伊朗的情況和俄羅斯非常相似，解決這些問題有兩個方案。他表示，除了他不願意使用的軍事選項外，另一個就是經濟方案――對俄羅斯施加壓力，打壓他們的能源出口。津克說：&ldquo;我們能做到這一點，因為美國是世界上最大的石油和天然氣生產國。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　俄羅斯連塔網稱，特朗普政府反對俄羅斯在歐洲的&ldquo;北溪-2&rdquo;能源項目，因為華盛頓認為，此項目將成為俄羅斯在該地區施加影響力的杠杆。俄方認為，特朗普旨在希望歐盟購買更多的美國天然氣。"},{"pid":"dc805138c2101943f0cb7815f4fb3202c319ce0c","tid":842304,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"民豬黨：通俄門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6532cfe89bd2738a25b772682b2f594472f5df","tid":842304,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:41:40.000Z","msg":"普京都郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4194fe2a5eb166724061203933b09f43ee2b2d22","tid":842304,"uid":64922,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc805138c2101943f0cb7815f4fb3202c319ce0c","tid":842304,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"民豬黨：通俄門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"其實侵侵當日選時有無通俄<br />\n同今日打俄佬兩回事<br />\n侵侵選贏左反轉豬肚好平常<br />\n<br />\n好似香港當日689咁<br />\n選時搵尖bear &amp; 上海仔咁<br />\n到贏左咪又反轉豬肚"},{"pid":"951dbf5c6e610421bcb436db9da6162739b5a4e8","tid":842304,"uid":4783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4194fe2a5eb166724061203933b09f43ee2b2d22","tid":842304,"uid":64922,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc805138c2101943f0cb7815f4fb3202c319ce0c","tid":842304,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"民豬黨：通俄門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"其實侵侵當日選時有無通俄<br />\n同今日打俄佬兩回事<br />\n侵侵選贏左反轉豬肚好平常<br />\n<br />\n好似香港當日689咁<br />\n選時搵尖bear &amp; 上海仔咁<br />\n到贏左咪又反轉豬肚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"但係dnc班傻鳩話侵上台做左好多favour俄佬既野嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家真係駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\